reviewText:
The great George Raft

What else is there to say?
George Raft is great in this. He is sharp and effective. His fans will love it. Otherwlse, the rest of the movie is ... a little flat unfortunately.
Great movie with great actors and a great plot.
Nearly every line of this movie from the characters has a double meaning as each tries to maneuver the other. Have to watch more than once to pick up all the nuances. Great script.
A great film noir.  A must have if you are a George Raft fan.  There was only one and loved his movies.
